{"type": "article", "id": 26115, "title": "延展式桑拿房", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-28T07:10:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070214402485JQOwKNHYkigRmP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">如果你有一个在家蒸桑拿的梦想，德国公司 <a href=\"http://www.klafs.com/\">Klafs</a> 最新推出的这款延展式桑拿房 S1 可以帮你美梦成真。S1 的大小和一个书柜相当，可延展的空间共有三层——按下控制面板上的按钮，只需 20 秒，60 厘米深的空间就能完全展开。S1 内部所使用的木材比普通桑拿房内使用的要轻上 40%，Klafs 还为它配备了一个镶嵌式的照明灯和几个可以通过蓝牙和手机连接的扬声器。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144022cm5NIdXK6goj0Gat.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65281174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144023tZnuzOI0yDPap1fl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144023TbDmrS9pwjUAxN47.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61246944\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144024etLXY57wlmKQF2S3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n"}